            <h1>Legal Aspect</h1>
            <p>Considering investors as a key factor for sustained economic growth, Morocco committed to the liberalization of its economy by easing the procedures, providing better protection to private operators by adopting new laws and granting investors great overall conditions; The overall aim is to capture a significant flow of national and foreign private assets.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary page-scroll" href="#code" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a>
